== Aho gahereye ==
[[Dosiye:Kigali Car Free Zone.jpg|alt=in Kigali|thumb|168x168px|Agace katarangwamo imodoka bita Car free zone gaherereye mu mujyi wa Kigali]]
Ni agace kava kuri KN 4 Ave gafite ahanini amabanki, butike zo mumujyi rwagati, amaduka yo mu nzu hamwe na bureaux. Umuhanda ukora kuri KN 78 Mutagatifu (Umuhanda wa Ecole Belge) na KN 84 Mutagatifu (munsi yumuhanda utagira imodoka) nawo wagize ingaruka kuri politiki yo guhagarika imodoka. [https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/ Abantu barashobora] kuboneka bagenda "hagati yumuhanda" inzira yose.<ref>https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/</ref>

== Ibihabera ==
[https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/ Umwanya] wabaye ahantu hatoranijwe kubategura ibirori nko guhurira hamwe, ibitaramo by'imyidagaduro, [https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/ imurikagurisha] ryubuhanzi n’amavuriro yimyororokere nibindi.

Mu Ihuriro ry’Ubukungu ku Isi (WEF) ryakiriwe muri uyu mujyi muri Gicurasi, amasosiyete menshi yakoresheje umwanya wo kwakira ibirori bitandukanye kugira ngo ashimishe intumwa za WEF gusa, ndetse n’abaturage baho.<ref name=":0">https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/</ref><ref name=":0" />

== Icyateganyijwe ==
Kigali n'umujyi ukura vuba utuwe na miliyoni 1.1. [https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/ Abategura umujyi] bashizeho ingamba zo gushyiraho imihanda mishya inyuze mu nkengero kugira ngo bakureho ibinyabiziga bitwara [https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/ abagenzi] ariko kandi bituma umujyi urinda umutekano w’abanyamaguru.<ref name=":1">https://africa.cgtn.com/2016/07/12/how-car-free-zones-in-rwandas-kigali-are-helping-the-city/</ref><ref name=":1" />

